replies.body:
have you ever played garen or trundle or maokai full tank? so much  fun idgaf what you have to say! give them grasp of the undying and fun is at your finger tips, stop worrying about things like, when to initiate, or...dying
and worry about things like, am i troll enough? does the enemy team hate me enough? should i fight them or run up to them, dance and run around while they chase me and my team cleans up objectives?

if u havent had tank troll fun yet, you sir, are missing out {{champion:48}}
